### Day 3–4: Ablations

#### Step 9: Dense Ablation
Create `config/rag_ablation_dense.yaml`:
```yaml
benchmark:
  name: swebench_lite
  split: test
  limit: 30

gatherers:
  - name: rag_dense
    model: all-MiniLM-L6-v2
    top_k: 20

k_values: [5, 10, 20]
dashboard:
  enabled: false
output_dir: ./results/ablation_dense
```
Run: `harness --config config/rag_ablation_dense.yaml`

